- Yes!
- Has it ever happened to you?

78
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:05,633
- No, never!
- And you others?

79
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:09,349
I consider it a waste of time
and a futile gesture.

80
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,634
Come on,
get out of my way!

81
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,950
