82
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,997
Victory will be mine!

83
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,837
We'll see!

84
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:28,433
Are you getting out
of the way or not!

85
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:32,640
Sempai, you need to do better.

86
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,473
You made an idiot of
yourself before the race...

87
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:37,949
...this is just the after effects!

88
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,674
This is all happening on purpose!

89
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:44,709
