97
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,836
Gunma!

98
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:38,909
- Impossible! I must be dreaming!
- I should have taken a picture!

99
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:42,670
- How did he do that?
- I don't know.

100
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:46,793
- I wonder how...!
- He's the best driver in the world!

101
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:49,952
- I can hardly believe my eyes!
- Hand me the glasses.

102
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,356
It's just me and you!

103
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,590
- Victory!
- Gunma, you're great!

104
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:45,636
Those are my glasses.

105
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,756
