109
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:10,480
Gunma, you've finally you made it!

110
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,596
You have won!

111
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:22,592
Wow!
Now that's a surprise!

112
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:25,439
