I expected as much.

148
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:35,194
That's just the way he is.

149
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:38,434
- Excuse him!
- What?

150
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:42,156
Gunma!
Have a drink with us..

151
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:45,550
