In fact, his driving has improved a lot.

164
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,868
But in the end what
matters most is still the car!

165
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,475
Hiziri.

166
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:33,756
I won't give up on you.

167
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:36,878
