health you shouldn't drive.

168
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:39,037
Please, forget it!

169
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:43,675
- In order to win I need you.
- But I...

170
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:46,269
Tomorrow morning we
leave for the next circuit.

171
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:49,238
I hope you've got the message.
I'm counting on you!

172
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:55,596
Bye, I'll see you there.

173
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:20,756
Gunma!

174
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:24,517
Oh, I'm sorry!
Hey you know,

175
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:26,875
Is this the way
to celebrate my victory?

176
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:31,076
Drinking a fourth beer in a tavern!

177
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:34,875
I would rather be in a fancy restaurant,

178
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:37,269
surrounded by beautiful girls!

179
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:41,549
- You really are a true champion!
- Your lovely!

180
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,517
Why don't we have some fun?

181
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,360
This is the way I
would like to celebrate!

182
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:51,158
