184
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:56,192
You know what? Thanks to
you, during the race,

185
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:59,750
- I seemed to be flying!
- I know!

186
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:02,354
Today you drove like a pro!

187
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:05,632
Our eyes were literally glued to you!

188
