It's Forbidden

246
00:22:14,150 --> 00:22:20,100
Freak-Out Tonight,
Dangerous Motion

247
00:22:20,100 --> 00:22:26,400
I want to forget that
lonely and loud me

248
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:36,200
Like Clockwork, don't be a
loner in the crowd

249
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:45,100
Don't you let
